<br>
When groups are looking for a tank, they are typically looking for a warrior, shadowknight or paladin.  Monks are tanks of necessity--when no plate tanks or, oftentimes, rangers or beastlords are available.<br>
<br>
I love my monk and wouldn't play any other class.  SOE has acknowledged that pure melee classes have fallen behind.<br>
